Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:42.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD 在絕望中握住僅存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:51.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用顫抖的手指瞄準目標 去追尋未來！
Comment: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDJP——————————————
