Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:58.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:03.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:08.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:13.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
