Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:19.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:24.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:26.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:29.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:34.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:37.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:39.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:47.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
