Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:37.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴隨著結尾即開始的詠嘆調
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:42.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高舉白旗的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:48.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃獄後的歡呼聲中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:52.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被強行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:58.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:03.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:08.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:13.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:13.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:16.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多線並行的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:19.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撥開人群
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊著 這是我正義的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:24.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:26.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得讚美的驚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:29.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯獨拒絕喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:34.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:37.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過於艷麗的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:39.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帶有偏見的分類
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信沒有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:43.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:47.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都愛著絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會滿懷悲傷地離去
